{"tid":1900586,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"AI 手塚治虫 新作","createTime":"2020-02-27T10:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T14:04:57.000Z","uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aa618a99d433e43db1d83451ebeeaa0745afb04c","tid":1900586,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"「漫畫之神」手塚治虫透過AI（人工智慧）推出新作品一一。在27日出刊的講談社青年漫畫雜誌《MORNING（日文為：モーニング）》上，刊載了1部新漫畫作品《Phaedo（日文為：ぱいどん）》，此為活用了學習過手塚治虫作品的AI所創作而成的漫畫。<br />\n<br />\n　　該漫畫是以2030年的東京為舞台，內容描述1名因逃離高度控制人民生活的社會而無家可歸的哲學家「Phaedo」，目標要解決事件的故事。而故事的粗略概要、主角的人物性格設定以及角色造型設計原案是由AI發想；詳細的情節及作畫則透過人類的手來完成，是1部由AI與人類共同創作的漫畫。<br />\n<br />\n　　此為半導體大廠鎧俠(Kioxia)與手塚製作公司(Tezuka Productions)等，以「若是1989年去世的手塚治虫到現在還活著並畫著漫畫的話」為概念所展開的企劃。而26日已舉行了作品的亮相儀式，手塚治虫的長男手塚真表示：「新的漫畫作品簡直就如同手塚治虫的世界。雖然還在發展途中，但這是能幫忙將漫畫文化留在未來的技術。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://asahichinese-f.com/cool_japan/anime/13169569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasahichinese-f.com%2Fcool_japan%2Fanime%2F13169569&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgQaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=c23568e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://asahichinese-f.com/cool_japan/anime/13169569</a>"},{"pid":"3efab174dc16f0669dbfa664707cdaeff4085640","tid":1900586,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcdbSKX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcdbSKX.png&h=bf7323bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb0512da23a7ef472570051da871b5024f08f2ab","tid":1900586,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6029f87ee8d67fe174fcc17853b37eb42cab61","tid":1900586,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"01 01 01 01"},{"pid":"d4bd006bf73106b14006a6e53831296885d3e334","tid":1900586,"uid":56684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"